data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Homestead! Nestled in a charming gated community, boasting 5 bedrooms/3 full baths. One bedroom and a full-size bathroom conveniently located on the 1st floor, this home is perfect for multi-generational living. Upstairs, you'll find 4 bedrooms, including the primary suite with a tub/stand-up shower. Each room is generously sized offering versatility. Step into the heart of this community, where residents enjoy exclusive access to a club house, community pool, and a state-of-the-art gym, perfect for healthy & active lifestyle. Outdoor enthusiasts will appreciate the new bike path in the area, offering a scenic route to explore the surroundings. Seller offers $7k incentives/credit towards Buyers' Closing costs or buydown interest. Motivated Seller!!
